title: Tacoma Food Co-Op

review.description: Ever improving neighborhood market!!! Be sure to check back often, they have an terrific selection of organic veggies, ...bulk Kambucha on tap, better prices then FM's bulk food section and...
I love this place! I sincerely can't wait until the Seckel / Sugar Pears come back -- please make sure you let us know when they make their appearance again!
